On the commencement of the month of Ramadaan, we wish the Muslim Community of South Africa and all Muslims around the world a blessed month.At this time of self-sacrifice where Muslims fast from sunrise to sunset, our support is with you.The DA recognises the caring, sharing and giving, which marks this period for all Muslims.It is a time of community, family, sharing food and breaking fast together, and we wish our Muslim brothers and sisters well during this time.On behalf of the DA, I wish all Muslims a spiritually fulfilling month.Our prayers, support and best wishes are with all of you.Ramadan Mubarak.